Page_0: "Task 1; There is a utility room which holds the main power switches for the building.  I must determine which switch cuts off power to the elevator, and then ensure that it stays off.  Once that is done, Agent Stone, who is on the roof, will be able to enter the building through the elevator’s shaft, and enter the casino’s vault."

Page_1: "Task 2;  I will need to find my way into the building’s main security control room.  Once inside, I will need to crack the pass code which will shut off the cameras both in the security room, and in the vault.  This will allow Agent Stone to enter the vault without having to worry about the unblinking eyes of the security cameras tripping any alarms."

Page_2: "Once I choose, I will be unable to change my mind.  I shouldn’t keep Sheam waiting; the team is counting on me."